paragraphs.title: S3T
paragraphs.text:
CYPHER runtime=interpreted 
UNWIND range(2,10) AS n
WITH toString(n) AS iN, "10000" as iM
MATCH (cl:CollectedProductArgNode {Dimension:'8',MaxN:iM,N:iN})-[:Arguments]->(aN:ArgumentsNode)
WITH max(aN.ResultDivisor) AS maxDivisor,iN,iM
MATCH (cl:CollectedProductArgNode {Dimension:'8',MaxN:iM,N:iN})-[:Arguments]->(aN:ArgumentsNode)
//RETURN aN.ScalarProduct,aN.DegreeSum,aN.ResultDivisor,cl.tft,cl.Divisor,iN,iM
WITH {DS:COLLECT({ResultScalar:aN.ScalarProduct, ResultDegree:aN.DegreeSum, ResultDivisor:aN.ResultDivisor}), ET:cl.tft, Divisor:cl.Divisor} AS resultProduct,iN,iM,maxDivisor
WITH COLLECT(resultProduct) as rPC,resultProduct.ET as eT,iN,iM,resultProduct.Divisor as rpD1,maxDivisor
UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(rPC)-1) as iI
WITH rPC[iI].DS as rPCDS,eT,iN,iM,rpD1,maxDivisor
UNWIND rPCDS as rPCDSU
WITH {RScalarList:COLLECT({RScalar:rPCDSU.ResultScalar}),RDegree:rPCDSU.ResultDegree,RDivisor:rPCDSU.ResultDivisor,ET:eT,Divisor:rpD1} as resultMap,iN,iM,maxDivisor
WITH COLLECT(resultMap) as resultMapC,resultMap.RDivisor as rDivisor,resultMap.ET as eTrm,resultMap.RDegree as rDRM,iN,iM,resultMap.Divisor as rpD2,maxDivisor
UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(resultMapC)-1) as iII
WITH resultMapC[iII].RScalarList as rSL,rDivisor,rDRM,iN,iM,rpD2,maxDivisor,eTrm
UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(rSL)-1) as iIII
UNWIND rSL[iIII] as rSLI
WITH COLLECT(apoc.number.exact.mul(rSLI.RScalar,apoc.number.exact.div(maxDivisor,rDivisor))) as cts,rDRM,iN,iM,rpD2,maxDivisor,eTrm 
WITH REDUCE(sum='0', x in cts | apoc.number.exact.add(sum,toString(x))) as acc,rDRM,iN,iM,rpD2,maxDivisor,eTrm
WITH {DSList:COLLECT({Degree:rDRM,Scalar:acc}),DivideBy:maxDivisor} AS pTerms,iM,iN,eTrm 
WITH COLLECT(pTerms) as pTermss,iM,iN,eTrm
UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(pTermss)-1) as pT
WITH pTermss[pT].DSList as dSList,iN,iM,pTermss[pT].DivideBy AS pTD,eTrm
UNWIND dSList as dSListU
WITH dSListU.Degree AS tDegree,dSListU.Scalar AS tScalar,iN,iM,pTD,eTrm
RETURN tDegree,tScalar,iN,iM,pTD,eTrm

paragraphs.title: S3A
paragraphs.text:
CYPHER runtime=interpreted 
UNWIND range(2,2) AS n
WITH toString(n) AS iN, "8" as iM
MATCH (v:VertexNode)<-[vI:VertexIndexedBy]-(i:IndexedBy {N:iN,MaxN:iM,Dimension:'8'})-[]->(e:Evaluate)
WITH iN, iM, max(vI.divisor) as maxDivisor
MATCH (v:VertexNode)<-[vI:VertexIndexedBy]-(i:IndexedBy {N:iN,MaxN:iM,Dimension:'8'})-[]->(e:Evaluate)
// return v.Scalar,v.Degree,vI.divisor,vI.twoSeq
WITH {DS:COLLECT({ResultScalar:v.Scalar, ResultDegree:v.Degree, ResultDivisor:vI.divisor}), Divisor:vI.twoSeq} AS resultProduct,iN,iM,maxDivisor

WITH COLLECT(resultProduct) as rPC,iN,iM,resultProduct.Divisor as rpD1,maxDivisor
UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(rPC)-1) as iI
WITH rPC[iI].DS as rPCDS,iN,iM,rpD1,maxDivisor
UNWIND rPCDS as rPCDSU
WITH {RScalarList:COLLECT({RScalar:rPCDSU.ResultScalar}),RDegree:rPCDSU.ResultDegree,RDivisor:rPCDSU.ResultDivisor,Divisor:rpD1} as resultMap,iN,iM,maxDivisor
WITH COLLECT(resultMap) as resultMapC,resultMap.RDivisor as rDivisor,resultMap.RDegree as rDRM,iN,iM,resultMap.Divisor as rpD2,maxDivisor
UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(resultMapC)-1) as iII
WITH resultMapC[iII].RScalarList as rSL,rDivisor,rDRM,iN,iM,rpD2,maxDivisor
UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(rSL)-1) as iIII
UNWIND rSL[iIII] as rSLI

//RETURN rSLI.RScalar,rDivisor,rDRM,iN,iM,maxDivisor
WITH COLLECT(apoc.number.exact.mul(rSLI.RScalar,apoc.number.exact.div(maxDivisor,rDivisor))) as cts,rDRM,iN,iM,rpD2,maxDivisor
WITH REDUCE(sum='0', x in cts | apoc.number.exact.add(sum,toString(x))) as acc,rDRM,iN,iM,rpD2,maxDivisor
WITH COLLECT(acc) as accc,rDRM,iN,iM,maxDivisor
WITH REDUCE(sum='0', x in accc | apoc.number.exact.add(sum,toString(x))) as acc,rDRM,iN,iM,maxDivisor
WITH {DSList:COLLECT({Degree:rDRM,Scalar:acc}),DivideBy:maxDivisor} AS pTerms,iM,iN 
WITH COLLECT(pTerms) as pTermss,iM,iN
UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(pTermss)-1) as pT
WITH pTermss[pT].DSList as dSList,iN,iM,pTermss[pT].DivideBy AS pTD
UNWIND dSList as dSListU
WITH dSListU.Degree AS aDegree,dSListU.Scalar AS aScalar,iN,iM,pTD
RETURN aDegree,aScalar,pTD,iM,iN

paragraphs.title: S3E
paragraphs.text:
CYPHER runtime=interpreted 
UNWIND range(2,12) AS n
WITH toString(n) AS iN, "10000" as iM
MATCH (v:VertexNode)<-[vI:VertexIndexedBy]-(i:IndexedBy {N:iN,MaxN:iM,Dimension:'8'})-[]->(e:Evaluate)
WITH iN, iM, max(vI.divisor) as maxDivisor
MATCH (v:VertexNode)<-[vI:VertexIndexedBy]-(i:IndexedBy {N:iN,MaxN:iM,Dimension:'8'})-[]->(e:Evaluate)
WITH {DS:COLLECT({ResultScalar:v.Scalar, ResultDegree:v.Degree, ResultDivisor:vI.divisor}), Divisor:vI.twoSeq} AS resultProduct,iN,iM,maxDivisor

WITH COLLECT(resultProduct) as rPC,iN,iM,resultProduct.Divisor as rpD1,maxDivisor
UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(rPC)-1) as iI
WITH rPC[iI].DS as rPCDS,iN,iM,rpD1,maxDivisor
UNWIND rPCDS as rPCDSU
WITH {RScalarList:COLLECT({RScalar:rPCDSU.ResultScalar}),RDegree:rPCDSU.ResultDegree,RDivisor:rPCDSU.ResultDivisor,Divisor:rpD1} as resultMap,iN,iM,maxDivisor
WITH COLLECT(resultMap) as resultMapC,resultMap.RDivisor as rDivisor,resultMap.RDegree as rDRM,iN,iM,resultMap.Divisor as rpD2,maxDivisor
UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(resultMapC)-1) as iII
WITH resultMapC[iII].RScalarList as rSL,rDivisor,rDRM,iN,iM,rpD2,maxDivisor
UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(rSL)-1) as iIII
UNWIND rSL[iIII] as rSLI

//RETURN rSLI.RScalar,rDivisor,rDRM,iN,iM,maxDivisor
WITH COLLECT(apoc.number.exact.mul(rSLI.RScalar,apoc.number.exact.div(maxDivisor,rDivisor))) as cts,rDRM,iN,iM,rpD2,maxDivisor
WITH REDUCE(sum='0', x in cts | apoc.number.exact.add(sum,toString(x))) as acc,rDRM,iN,iM,rpD2,maxDivisor
WITH COLLECT(acc) as accc,rDRM,iN,iM,maxDivisor
WITH REDUCE(sum='0', x in accc | apoc.number.exact.add(sum,toString(x))) as acc,rDRM,iN,iM,maxDivisor
WITH {DSList:COLLECT({Degree:rDRM,Scalar:acc}),DivideBy:maxDivisor} AS pTerms,iM,iN 
WITH COLLECT(pTerms) as pTermss,iM,iN
UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(pTermss)-1) as pT
WITH pTermss[pT].DSList as dSList,iN,iM,pTermss[pT].DivideBy AS pTD
UNWIND dSList as dSListU

WITH REDUCE(sum='1', x in RANGE(1,toInteger(dSListU.Degree)) | apoc.number.exact.mul(sum,toString(iM))) as acc,iN,iM,dSListU,pTD
With apoc.number.exact.mul(dSListU.Scalar,acc) as scalarDegreeProduct,iN,iM,pTD
WITH {SDP:COLLECT(scalarDegreeProduct),DivideBy:toString(pTD)} as termsMap,iN,iM
WITH COLLECT(termsMap) AS termsMapC,iN,iM
UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(termsMapC)-1) AS pTT
WITH REDUCE(sum='0', x IN termsMapC[pTT].SDP | apoc.number.exact.add(sum,toString(x))) AS acc,toString(termsMapC[pTT].DivideBy) AS dB,iM,iN
WITH apoc.number.exact.div(acc,dB) AS pResult,acc,dB,iM,iN
WITH COLLECT(pResult) AS evaluates,iN,iM
WITH REDUCE (sum='0', n IN evaluates| apoc.number.exact.add(sum,n)) AS acc 
RETURN acc as Value

paragraphs.title: S12Initial (json)
paragraphs.text:
CYPHER runtime=interpreted 
        UNWIND range(toInteger(?),toInteger(?)) AS n
        WITH toString(n) AS N, ? as nMax
        MATCH (v:VertexNode)<-[]-(i:IndexedBy)-[]->(e:Evaluate),(t:TwoSeqFactor)<-[]-(i) where i.N=N AND i.MaxN=nMax AND i.Dimension=? AND t.twoSeq=? 
        WITH i.N as iN, i.MaxN as iM,e,v,t,i                       
        OPTIONAL MATCH (vv:VertexNode)<-[]-(ii:IndexedBy)-[]->(ee:Evaluate {Value:toString(t.twoSeq)}),(tt:TwoSeqFactor)<-[]-(ii) where ii.MaxN=iM  AND ii.Dimension=?
        WITH
        '1'  AS pDivisor, 
        '2' AS pDimension,
        '2' AS vDivisor,
        tt.twoSeq AS vvTwoSeq,
        ee.Value AS eeValue,
        '2'  AS vvDivisor,
         i,      //iN,
        '4' AS iDimension,
               // iM,
        t.twoSeq AS vTwoSeq,
        v.Degree AS vDegree,
        vv.Degree AS vvDegree,
        v.Scalar AS vScalar,
        vv.Scalar AS vvScalar,  
        toString( CASE WHEN toString(i.RowCounter)='2' THEN apoc.number.exact.mul(toString(v.Scalar),'2') ELSE toString(v.Scalar) END ) AS q
        WITH
        i,pDivisor as pD,vTwoSeq,vvDegree,vvScalar,vDivisor,vvDivisor,vvTwoSeq,       //  N,iM    *****    vTwoSeq as pD
        CASE WHEN vvScalar IS null THEN 99 ELSE  toInteger(eeValue) END as p2Eval,
             toString( CASE WHEN toString(vDegree)='-1' THEN apoc.number.exact.mul(toString(vScalar),'2') ELSE toString(TTScalarRowCounter) END ) AS TTScalar,
             toString( CASE WHEN toString(vvDegree)='-1' THEN apoc.number.exact.mul(toString(vvScalar),'2') ELSE apoc.number.exact.mul(toString(vvScalar),vvTwoSeq) END) AS AAScalar,     
             toString( CASE WHEN toString(vDegree)='-1' THEN apoc.number.exact.add(vDegree,'1') ELSE apoc.number.exact.add(vDegree,'0') END ) AS TTDegree,
             toString( CASE WHEN toString(vvDegree)='-1' THEN apoc.number.exact.add(vvDegree,'1') ELSE apoc.number.exact.add(vvDegree,'0')  END) AS AADegree
        
        WITH {iN:i.N,iM:i.MaxN,pD:pD,vTwoSeq:vTwoSeq,vDivisor:vDivisor,vvDivisor:vvDivisor,vvTwoSeq:CASE WHEN vvTwoSeq IS NULL THEN \"0\" ELSE vvTwoSeq END,p2Eval:p2Eval,
               TTScalar:TTScalar,AAScalar:CASE WHEN AAScalar IS NULL THEN \"0\" ELSE AAScalar END,TTDegree:TTDegree,AADegree:CASE WHEN AADegree IS NULL THEN \"0\" ELSE AADegree END,
               degreeSum:CASE WHEN vvDegree IS Null THEN TTDegree ELSE apoc.number.exact.add(TTDegree,AADegree) END,
               scalarProduct:CASE WHEN vvScalar IS Null THEN toString(TTScalar) ELSE apoc.number.exact.mul(TTScalar,AAScalar) END,
               resultDivisor:CASE WHEN vvScalar IS Null THEN toString(vDivisor) ELSE apoc.number.exact.mul( toString(vDivisor),apoc.number.exact.mul(toString(vvDivisor),toString(pD))) END,
               writeDimension:?} as lines
        RETURN lines

paragraphs.title: S12Recurring
paragraphs.text:
CYPHER runtime=interpreted 
        UNWIND range(toInteger(?),toInteger(?)) AS n
        WITH toString(n) AS N, ? as nMax
        MATCH (v:VertexNode {Degree:?})<-[vI:VertexIndexedBy {twoSeq:?}]-(i:IndexedBy {N:N,MaxN:nMax,Dimension:?})-[]->(e:Evaluate)
        WITH i.N as iN, i.MaxN as iM,e,v,vI,i                        
        OPTIONAL MATCH (vv:VertexNode)<-[vII:VertexIndexedBy]-(ii:IndexedByArgument)-[]->(ee:Evaluate {Value:toString(vI.twoSeq)})      
                            where ii.MaxN=iM  AND ii.Dimension=?
        
        WITH
        vI.twoSeq AS vTwoSeq,
        vI.divisor AS vDivisor,
        vII.twoSeq AS vvTwoSeq,
        ee.Value AS eeValue,
        vII.divisor AS vvDivisor,
        iN,
        iM,
        i.Dimension AS iDimension,
        v.Scalar AS vScalar,
        v.Degree AS vDegree,
        vv.Scalar AS vvScalar,
        vv.Degree AS vvDegree,i
                                            
        WITH
        
        iN,iM,vTwoSeq as pD,vTwoSeq,vvDegree,vvScalar,vDivisor,vvDivisor,vvTwoSeq,  
        CASE WHEN vvScalar IS null THEN 99 ELSE  toInteger(eeValue) END as p2Eval,
             toString( CASE WHEN toString(vDegree)='-1' THEN apoc.number.exact.mul(toString(vScalar),'2') ELSE toString(vScalar) END ) AS TTScalar,
        toString( CASE WHEN toString(vvDegree)='-1' THEN apoc.number.exact.mul(toString(vvScalar),'2') ELSE toString(vvScalar) END) AS AAScalar,
        toString( CASE WHEN toString(vDegree)='-1' THEN apoc.number.exact.add(vDegree,'1') ELSE apoc.number.exact.add(vDegree,'0') END ) AS TTDegree,
        toString( CASE WHEN toString(vvDegree)='-1' THEN apoc.number.exact.add(vvDegree,'1') ELSE apoc.number.exact.add(vvDegree,'0')  END) AS AADegree
        
        WITH
        {iM:iM,iN:iN,pD:pD,p2Eval:p2Eval,vTwoSeq:vTwoSeq,TTDegree:TTDegree,TTScalar:TTScalar,vDivisor:vDivisor,vvDivisor:vvDivisor,vvTwoSeq:vvTwoSeq,AADegree:AADegree,AAScalar:AAScalar,
        degreeSum:CASE WHEN vvDegree IS Null THEN TTDegree ELSE apoc.number.exact.add(TTDegree,AADegree) END,
        scalarProduct:CASE WHEN vvScalar IS Null THEN toString(TTScalar) ELSE apoc.number.exact.mul(TTScalar,AAScalar) END,
        resultDivisor:CASE WHEN vvScalar IS Null THEN toString(vDivisor) ELSE apoc.number.exact.mul( toString(vDivisor),apoc.number.exact.mul(toString(vvDivisor),toString(pD))) END,
        writeDimension:?} AS line
        RETURN line

paragraphs.title: S3ARC  -   P(MaxN,N,D,RowCounter) from IndexedBy pattern.
paragraphs.text:
CYPHER runtime=interpreted
        UNWIND range(toInteger('5'),toInteger('5')) AS n
        WITH toString(n) AS iN, '8' as iM
        MATCH (v:VertexNode)<-[vI:VertexIndexedBy]-(i:IndexedBy {N:iN,MaxN:iM,Dimension:'8',RowCounter:8})-[]->(e:Evaluate)
        WITH iN, iM, max(vI.divisor) as maxDivisor
        MATCH (v:VertexNode)<-[vI:VertexIndexedBy]-(i:IndexedBy {N:iN,MaxN:iM,Dimension:'8',RowCounter:8})-[]->(e:Evaluate)
        // return v.Scalar,v.Degree,vI.divisor,vI.twoSeq
        WITH {DS:COLLECT({ResultScalar:v.Scalar, ResultDegree:v.Degree, ResultDivisor:vI.divisor}), Divisor:vI.twoSeq} AS resultProduct,iN,iM,maxDivisor
        
        WITH COLLECT(resultProduct) as rPC,iN,iM,resultProduct.Divisor as rpD1,maxDivisor
        UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(rPC)-1) as iI
        WITH rPC[iI].DS as rPCDS,iN,iM,rpD1,maxDivisor
        UNWIND rPCDS as rPCDSU
        WITH {RScalarList:COLLECT({RScalar:rPCDSU.ResultScalar}),RDegree:rPCDSU.ResultDegree,RDivisor:rPCDSU.ResultDivisor,Divisor:rpD1} as resultMap,iN,iM,maxDivisor
        WITH COLLECT(resultMap) as resultMapC,resultMap.RDivisor as rDivisor,resultMap.RDegree as rDRM,iN,iM,resultMap.Divisor as rpD2,maxDivisor
        UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(resultMapC)-1) as iII
        WITH resultMapC[iII].RScalarList as rSL,rDivisor,rDRM,iN,iM,rpD2,maxDivisor
        UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(rSL)-1) as iIII
        UNWIND rSL[iIII] as rSLI
        
        //RETURN rSLI.RScalar,rDivisor,rDRM,iN,iM,maxDivisor
        WITH COLLECT(apoc.number.exact.mul(rSLI.RScalar,apoc.number.exact.div(maxDivisor,rDivisor))) as cts,rDRM,iN,iM,rpD2,maxDivisor
        WITH REDUCE(sum='0', x in cts | apoc.number.exact.add(sum,toString(x))) as acc,rDRM,iN,iM,rpD2,maxDivisor
        WITH COLLECT(acc) as accc,rDRM,iN,iM,maxDivisor
        WITH REDUCE(sum='0', x in accc | apoc.number.exact.add(sum,toString(x))) as acc,rDRM,iN,iM,maxDivisor
        WITH {DSList:COLLECT({Degree:rDRM,Scalar:acc}),DivideBy:maxDivisor} AS pTerms,iM,iN 
        WITH COLLECT(pTerms) as pTermss,iM,iN
        UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(pTermss)-1) as pT
        WITH pTermss[pT].DSList as dSList,iN,iM,pTermss[pT].DivideBy AS pTD
        UNWIND dSList as dSListU
        WITH dSListU.Degree AS aDegree,dSListU.Scalar AS aScalar,iN,iM,pTD
        RETURN aDegree,aScalar,pTD,iM,iN

%neo4j
CYPHER runtime=interpreted
UNWIND range(7,7) AS n
WITH toString(n) AS N, "8" as nMax
MATCH (cl:CollectedProductArgNode {Dimension:'4',MaxN:nMax,N:N,tft:2})-[:Arguments]->(aN:ArgumentsNode)
With max(aN.ResultDivisor) as maxDivisor,N,nMax
MATCH (cl:CollectedProductArgNode {Dimension:'4',MaxN:nMax,N:N,tft:2})-[:Arguments]->(aN:ArgumentsNode)
WITH {Divisor:cl.Divisor,afe:cl.afe,tft:cl.tft,DS: COLLECT( {  TDegree:aN.TDegree,
      TScalar:aN.TScalar,TDivisor:aN.TDivisor,ADivisor:aN.ADivisor,ATwoSeq:aN.ATwoSeq,
      ADegree:aN.ADegree,AScalar:aN.AScalar,DegreeSum:aN.DegreeSum,ScalarProduct:aN.ScalarProduct,
      ResultDivisor:aN.ResultDivisor})}  AS argumentProduct,  N as iN, nMax as iM,maxDivisor  // cl.N as iN,cl.MaxN as iM,
WITH COLLECT(argumentProduct) as argumentProductt,argumentProduct.tft as aPafe,iN,iM,argumentProduct.Divisor as apD,argumentProduct.afe AS aPclafe,maxDivisor
UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(argumentProductt)-1) as iii
WITH argumentProductt[iii].DS as aPTds,aPafe,iN,iM,apD,aPclafe,maxDivisor
UNWIND aPTds as aPTdsU
//RETURN aPTdsU.ScalarProduct,aPTdsU.TScalar,aPTdsU.AScalar,aPTdsU.TDivisor,aPTdsU.ADivisor,aPTdsU.ADegree,aPTdsU.TDegree,aPTdsU.ResultDivisor,aPafe,iN,iM,apD,aPclafe,maxDivisor
WITH CASE WHEN aPclafe = 99 THEN                                                                                 
{DS:COLLECT({ResultScalar:aPTdsU.ScalarProduct,                                                                               
      ResultDegree:aPTdsU.DegreeSum,
      ResultDivisor:aPTdsU.ResultDivisor}),ET:aPafe,Divisor:apD}                                                                                                               
ELSE
{DS:COLLECT({ResultScalar:aPTdsU.ScalarProduct,                       
    ResultDegree:aPTdsU.DegreeSum,                              //CASE WHEN aPTdsU.ADegree=-1 THEN aPTdsU.TDegree ELSE apoc.number.exact.add(aPTdsU.ADegree,aPTdsU.TDegree) END,        
    ResultDivisor:aPTdsU.ResultDivisor}),ET:aPafe,Divisor:apD}
END
AS resultProduct,iN,iM,maxDivisor
//RETURN resultProduct
WITH COLLECT(resultProduct) as rPC,resultProduct.ET as eT,iN,iM,resultProduct.Divisor as rpD1,maxDivisor
UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(rPC)-1) as iI
WITH rPC[iI].DS as rPCDS,eT,iN,iM,rpD1,maxDivisor
UNWIND rPCDS as rPCDSU
WITH {RScalarList:COLLECT({RScalar:rPCDSU.ResultScalar}),RDegree:rPCDSU.ResultDegree,RDivisor:rPCDSU.ResultDivisor,ET:eT,Divisor:rpD1} as resultMap,iN,iM,maxDivisor
WITH COLLECT(resultMap) as resultMapC,resultMap.RDivisor as rDivisor,resultMap.ET as eTrm,resultMap.RDegree as rDRM,iN,iM,resultMap.Divisor as rpD2,maxDivisor
UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(resultMapC)-1) as iII
WITH resultMapC[iII].RScalarList as rSL,rDivisor,rDRM,iN,iM,rpD2,maxDivisor,eTrm
UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(rSL)-1) as iIII
UNWIND rSL[iIII] as rSLI
//RETURN rSLI.RScalar,rDivisor,rDRM,iN,iM,maxDivisor,eTrm
WITH COLLECT(rSLI.RScalar) as cts,rDivisor,rDRM,iN,iM,rpD2,"0" as accumulator,maxDivisor
CREATE (a:Accumulator { acc:"0"})
FOREACH (n IN cts| SET a.acc = apoc.number.exact.add(a.acc,n))  // Divisor (aka rowCounter)
WITH {DSList:COLLECT({Degree:rDRM,Scalar:a.acc}),DivideBy:rDivisor} AS pTerms,iM,iN 
//WITH {DSList:COLLECT({Degree:rDRM,Scalar:apoc.number.exact.mul(a.acc,apoc.number.exact.div(maxDivisor,rDivisor))}),DivideBy:maxDivisor} AS pTerms,iM,iN
//RETURN pTerms
WITH COLLECT(pTerms) as pTermss,iM,iN
UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(pTermss)-1) as pT
WITH pTermss[pT].DSList as dSList,iN,iM,pTermss[pT].DivideBy AS pTD
UNWIND dSList as dSListU
//RETURN dSListU.Degree,dSListU.Scalar,pTD
CREATE (c:Accumulator {acc:"1"})   
FOREACH (n IN RANGE(1,toInteger(dSListU.Degree))| SET c.acc = apoc.number.exact.mul(c.acc,toString(iM)))   //  dSListU.Degree must be integer
With apoc.number.exact.mul(dSListU.Scalar,c.acc) as scalarDegreeProduct,pTD,iN,iM
WITH {SDP:COLLECT(scalarDegreeProduct),DivideBy:toString(pTD)} as termsMap,iN,iM
//Return termsMap
WITH COLLECT(termsMap) AS termsMapC,iN,iM
UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(termsMapC)-1) as pTT
CREATE (b:Accumulator { acc:"0" ,db:toString(termsMapC[pTT].DivideBy) })
FOREACH (n IN termsMapC[pTT].SDP| SET b.acc = apoc.number.exact.add(b.acc,n))
WITH apoc.number.exact.div(b.acc,toString(b.db)) AS pResult,b,iM,iN

WITH COLLECT(pResult) as evaluates,iN,iM
//return evaluates,iN,iM
CREATE (d:Accumulator { acc:"0"})
FOREACH (n IN evaluates| SET d.acc = apoc.number.exact.add(d.acc,n)) 
RETURN d.acc as Value

paragraphs.text:
%neo4j

// Arithmetic Script
// Select x of the quadratic as i.MaxN from available list of nodes:  4,5,6,7,8,9,10,15,20,30,40,50,100,200,300,400,500
// Select two values to be added as string i.N with value = 2^(i.N-2) N>1 and N less then MaxN
// eg. i.N="4" or i.N="5" adds  2^2 + 2^3 as a graph representing quadratics evaluated at x=100 of value= 4 and 8
// Select a single i.N value for quadratic expression

CYPHER runtime=interpreted
MATCH (v:VertexNode)<-[]-(i:IndexedBy)-[]->(e:Evaluate),(t:TwoSeqFactor)<-[]-(i) WHERE (i.N="7" OR i.N="7") AND (i.MaxN="8") AND (i.Dimension="2")
WITH {TwoSeq:COLLECT({TwoSeq:toInteger(t.twoSeq)}),Vertex:v.Vertex} as factors,v,i,i.MaxN as iMax
WITH COLLECT(v.Vertex) as vV,factors,v,i,iMax
WITH COLLECT(factors.TwoSeq) as fact,v,i.N as N,vV,iMax
UNWIND RANGE(0,SIZE(fact)-1) as ii
UNWIND fact[ii] as ts
WITH collect(ts.TwoSeq) as cts,v,N,vV,iMax
WITH REDUCE(tSum=0,ff IN cts | tSum +ff) As TotalTseq,v,N,vV,iMax
WITH [v.Vertex,TotalTseq,N] as output,v,N,TotalTseq,vV,iMax
WITH {vVertex:v.Vertex,TotalT:TotalTseq,N:N} as outputMap,output,vV,iMax
WITH collect(output) as outputlist,outputMap,output,vV,iMax
WITH DISTINCT vV as vVV, outputlist,outputMap,output,iMax
WITH collect(outputMap.TotalT) as opMTT,vVV,iMax
WITH REDUCE(tSum=0,ff IN opMTT | tSum +ff) As TotalTseqq,opMTT,vVV,iMax
WITH Collect(TotalTseqq) as result,vVV,iMax

//Return {Multiple:result,Vertex:vVV} //  Uncomment and for instance: {"Vertex":"1 1 2 0 0","Degree":"2","Scalar":"1"}  are the Polynomial terms processed below 

UNWIND vVV as vVVV
WITH vVVV as lL,result as d,iMax
WITH lL,Size(lL) AS lLS,d,iMax                    
WITH lL,lLS-2 AS lLss,d,iMax                     
WITH SUBSTRING(lL,1,lLss) AS lLs,d,iMax          
WITH COLLECT(split(lLs,' ')) AS lList,d,iMax              

UNWIND RANGE(0,size(lList)-1) AS rC 
WITH  lList[rC] as vtx,d,iMax
WITH collect( toInteger((d[0]*(CASE WHEN toInteger(vtx[2])=-1 THEN toInteger(vtx[1])*2 ELSE toInteger(vtx[1]) END*(toInteger(iMax) ^ CASE WHEN toInteger(vtx[2])=-1 THEN toInteger(vtx[2])+1 ELSE toInteger(vtx[2]) END )))/2))  as rSlt
WITH REDUCE(tSum=0,ff IN rSlt  | tSum +ff) As TotalrSlt
RETURN TotalrSlt
